dataIdInfo.idPurp: This data was created to assist governmental agencies and others in making resource management decisions through the use of a Geographic Information System (GIS).
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This dataset contains a point location for each park in Mecklenburg County. Dataset includes parks managed by Mecklenburg County and the towns of Cornelius, Davidson, Huntersville, Matthews, Mint Hill, and Pineville.
